               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡, Mystagogia. ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, Prayer “For the Sake of Peaceful, Holy Things,” በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡, Anaphora of Our Lord Jesus Christ. Qäddase ´Ǝgzi’, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡, Sword of Divinity, ሠይፈ፡ መለኮት፡, Anaphora of Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bähänsa, ቅዳሴ" ማርያም", Office Prayers, Symbolic Interpretation of the Order of the Church, in Amharic, Monastic Writings, The Death of Moses, Rituals for the Unction of the Sick and Penitential Baptism, Greetings to Gäbrä Mänfäs Qəddus, Litanical Hymnsv</summary>
